business_definition: Group item containing the unique key fields for pending authorization record composed of authorization date and time
Authorization date in compressed numeric format (USAGE COMP-3)
Authorization time in compressed numeric format (USAGE COMP-3)
Original authorization date in character format
Original authorization time in character format
Credit or debit card number used for the authorization transaction
Authorization type code indicating the category of authorization request
Card expiration date in MMYY format
Type of authorization message received from the payment network
Source system or network that originated the authorization message
Authorization identification code assigned to the transaction
Authorization response code indicating approval or decline status
Condition indicating authorization was approved (VALUE '00')
Reason code providing additional detail for the authorization response
Processing code defining the type of transaction being authorized
Transaction amount requested for authorization (USAGE COMP-3)
Amount approved by the authorization system (USAGE COMP-3)
Merchant category code classifying the type of merchant business
Acquirer country code identifying the country of the acquiring institution
Point of sale entry mode indicating how card data was captured
Unique identifier assigned to the merchant location
Name of the merchant where the transaction was attempted
City where the merchant is located
State or province code where the merchant is located
Postal or ZIP code of the merchant location
Unique transaction identifier for tracking and reconciliation
Status code indicating the matching state of the pending authorization
Condition indicating authorization is pending match with transaction (VALUE 'P')
Condition indicating authorization was declined (VALUE 'D')
Condition indicating pending authorization has expired (VALUE 'E')
Condition indicating authorization has been matched with a transaction (VALUE 'M')
Fraud indicator flag for the authorization transaction
Condition indicating fraud has been confirmed on this authorization (VALUE 'F')
Condition indicating fraud flag has been removed from this authorization (VALUE 'R')
Date when fraud was reported for this authorization
Reserved placeholder field used for data structure alignment, padding, or holding constant values
